                <c>&lt;=</c> for <m>\leq</m>.)
              </instruction>
              <p>
                <var name="$setbuilder" width="12"/>
              </p>
            </statement>
            <solution>
              <p>
                <md>
                  <mrow><var name="$solleft[0]"/><var name="$sign"/><var name="$solright[0]"/></mrow>
                  <mrow><var name="$solleft[1]"/><var name="$sign"/><var name="$solright[1]"/></mrow>
                  <mrow><var name="$solleft[2]"/><var name="$oppsign"/><var name="$solright[2]"/></mrow>
                  <mrow><var name="$var"/><var name="$oppsign"/><var name="$sol"/></mrow>
                </md>
                So in set-builder notation, the solution set is <m><var name="$setbuilder"/></m>.
              </p>
